    "detail": "I heard place was only opened last year and it certainly looks quite new and facilities look more like a business or capsule hotel than guest house. I stayed in a capsule shared with many others in the room. Has central aircon and each capsule also has ventilation fan as well as small TV. Everyone were quiet at night so as long as you dont have someone snoring it can be pleasant sleep. Highlight has to be the onsen bath that you can use at most times and they also include free toiletries, towel and even bath robe and pants you can wear during the stay. Wifi was also quite good both in the room as well as in the common area. If you are interested the common room also has microwave, water, kettle and manga comic books also free to use",
